title: Big Take: Wall Street Money Cannon Lures Junior Bankers
itunes:title: Big Take: Wall Street Money Cannon Lures Junior Bankers
description:
Sridhar Natarajan, Bloomberg Senior Finance Reporter, discusses his Big Take story, "Wall Street Brings Out the Money Cannon to Lure Junior Bankers." Frank Rybinski, Chief Macro Strategist at Aegon Asset Management, talks markets and macro outlook. Todd Cipperman, Founding Principal of Cipperman Compliance Services, discusses the SEC's crypto regulation. Danielle DiMartino Booth, CEO and Chief Strategist for Quill Intelligence, talks markets and the Fed. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Matt Miller.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
